{"tid":1973462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"17歲男生管攻擊性武器    張潔宜署理主任裁判官：守法意職薄弱判入勞教中心","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T21:09:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbf7867a8e46f675556bc63efbd261924651e58","tid":1973462,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WHNamRBd2lkiSW3iSU8B.g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200415a151125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWHNamRBd2lkiSW3iSU8B.g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200415a151125.jpg&h=025fd437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年11月11日凌晨，17歲男學生在屯門澤豐街逃避警方追截，期間沿路「棄裝」，遺下汽油彈及鐵鎚被捕，他早前承認一項在公眾地方，裁判官今在屯門裁判法院判刑時接納報告建議，認為被告守法意職薄弱才犯案，判處被告進入勞教中心。<br />\n<br />\n張潔宜署理主任裁判官判刑時指，17歲蔡梓傑男學生所觸犯罪行一般須判處入獄，故不接納以感化令判刑。被告2019年終止中學學業，同年報讀青年學院課程，相信他犯案原於守法意職薄弱。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，去年11月11日凌晨近5時，警方接報有人在破壞輕鐵銀圍站，執勤間在青松觀見到有3名男子正在攀欄，被告見到警察隨即逃跑。被告先後放棄一個裝有汽油的灰色背囊和鐵鎚，惟最終制服被捕。"},{"pid":"bf1e1fdf8014b9a4bf0e48e0b73675d9ba29e299","tid":1973462,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fbf7867a8e46f675556bc63efbd261924651e58","tid":1973462,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WHNamRBd2lkiSW3iSU8B.g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200415a151125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWHNamRBd2lkiSW3iSU8B.g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDgwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200415a151125.jpg&h=025fd437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年11月11日凌